<!-- System Diagram -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Architecture</div>
    <h2>How the System Works</h2>
<pre>tokens.ts ──→ tokens.css ──→ brand/dist/tokens.css
     │                                │
     ▼                                ▼
templates/*.html  ──→  pdf.ts/image.ts  ──→  PDFs / PNGs
     │
     ▼
site/*.njk  ──→  11ty  ──→  brand/dist/site/  ──→  website /brand/  (via git submodule)</pre>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-body); margin-top: 16px;">
      <code>tokens.ts</code> is the single source of truth. Every template, document, and social asset sources its colors and fonts from there via CSS custom properties. Changes propagate automatically on the next build.
    </p>
  </div>
